> **Purpose.** A running log of LOCKED decisions on this project - architecture,
> scope, pricing, tooling, design, anything. Each decision is a dated entry.
> Entries are append-only; if a decision is reversed or superseded, add a NEW
> entry that supersedes the old one - do not delete history.
>
> Decisions that are still OPEN belong in `_resume.md` Section 13 (open threads),
> not here. This file holds only decisions that have been locked.
>
> **Contrast with other living files:**
> - `_living_project.md` - what the project IS
> - `_living_goals.md` - what the project aims for
> - `_living_design.md` - HOW the system is shaped
> - `_living_decisions.md` - choices that got made, and why (this file)

